Ngenhloso yokusimamisa umnotho waseNtshonalanga Kapa nowendawo eSogwini Olusentshonalanga, sesethule Isifunda Sokuthuthukiswa Kwezimboni sase-Saldanha futhi savula namafemu amabili e-Atlantis.
