Ukuze sikwazi ukunqoba inselelo yobubha kubantu bonke ngokuhlukahlukana kwabo, kumele sihlinzeke ngamakhono futhi sakhe amathuba omsebenzi abhekiswe kubantu abakhubazekile.
Ngakho-ke kuyinto ekhathazayo kakhulu ukuthi kukhona izingane ezikhubazekile ezilinganiselwa kwisigamu sesigidi okufanele ngabe zisesikoleni, kodwa njengamanje ezingafundi, ezihleli emakhaya.
Ngenhloso yokubhekana nalezi zinselelo, umsebenzi wokuhlelwa nokulawulwa kwezinhlelo eziphathelene nokukhubazeka usufakwe ngaphansi kweHhovisi likaMongameli.
Sesilivuselelile iThimba likaMongameli Elengamele Imisebenzi Ephathelene Nokukhubazeka, futhi kulo nyaka sizothumela ePhalamende iSivumelwano Samalungelo Abantu Abakhubazekile kwelase-Afrika, ukuze siqinisekiswe futhi samukelwe ngokusemthethweni.
Ngenhloso yokuxazulula izinkinga zabantu abasebenzayo abadla imbuya ngothi, sekuphele izinyanga eziyisithupha uqalile ukusebenza umholo ophansi kazwelonke, futhi izinkomba-kusebenza zalesi sikhashana esincane uqalile ukusebenza zibonisa ukuthi izinkampani eziningi ziyawuthobela.
IKhomishana Yomholo Ophansi Kazwelonke kulindeleke ukuthi iluphothule ngaphambi kokuphela kwenyanga kaMandulo 2019 ucwaningo mayelana nomthelela womholo ophansi kazwelonke ekuqashweni kwabantu, ububha, ukungalingani kanye nokuhluka kwemiholo.
Ngeke neze sikwazi ukuguqula isimo sezwe uma singagxili kakhulu ekukhulisweni komnotho.
Kule minyaka eyi-10 ezayo, sifuna ukuqinisekisa ukuthi umnotho ukhula ngesivinini esingaphezulu kakhulu kwesivinini sokukhula kwesibalo sabantu ezweni.
Futhi uma sesifinyelele emazingeni aphakeme okukhula komnotho ngokuqhubekayo yilapho-ke siyokwazi ukuguqula umonakalo wezomnotho owenzeke kuleli esikhathini esedlule.
Sikusho lokhu esikhathini lapho izibikezelo zesimo somnotho zibonisa isimo esibuthakathaka kakhulu.
Kulandela ukwehla nokuncipha kakhulu komnotho ngekota yokuqala yonyaka, manje ibhangengodla selibikezela ukuthi ngowezi-2019 umnotho kungenzeka ukhule ngezinga elingaphansi kwalelo elashiwo kwisabelomali esethulwa ngoNhlolanja.
Esinye sezizathu ezabangela ukufadalala komnotho wumthelela wokucinywa kukagesi ngenhloso yokuwonga ngasekuqaleni kwalo nyaka, kuhlangene nongabazane olulokhu luqhubeke njalo mayelana nokuphakelwa kukagesi kanye nesimo sezinto ebesingesihle kwa-Eskom.
Isifundo esisithola kulokhu sicace bha: ukuze sikwazi ukukhulisa umnotho, sidinga ukuphakelwa kukagesi okuqhubekayo, ngaso sonke isikhathi, futhi ngendlela esimeme.
U-Eskom ubhekene nezinkinga ezinkulu kwezezimali, ekuqhutshweni komsebenzi kanye nesimo sonkana ngaphakathi enkampanini.
Emva kokumiswa kohlelo lokucinywa kukagesi ngenhloso yokuwonga ngasekuqaleni kwalo nyaka, u-Eskom usenze inqubekelaphambili enkulu impela ekuqalisweni koHlelo Olunamaphuzu Ayisishiyagalolunye, ekuqinisekiseni ukulungiswa nokugcinwa kweziphehla-mandla za-Eskom zisebenza kahle, ekuncishisweni kwezindleko kanye nasekuqinisekiseni ukuthi kunamalahle agciniwe anele.
Ngokuhambisana nezincomo zeThimba Elengamele Umsebenzi Wokuqinisekisa Ukusimama kuka-Eskom kanjalo neThimba Lokubuyekeza Umsebenzi ka-Eskom, u-Eskom uzothumela labo basebenzi bakhe abanekhono kanye nolwazi lomsebenzi olunzulu namava ezindaweni lapho bedingeka khona kakhulu.
Isimo sezimali sale nkampani siyinto elokhu iqhubeke njalo nokudala ukukhathazeka okukhulu.
Njengoba kukhona isamba semali ebekwe eceleni esivela kuhulumeni esamenyezelwa kwisabelomali sowezi-2019, u-Eskom unemali eyanele ezokwenza akwazi ukuqhuba imisebenzi yakhe kanye nokukhokhela izikweletu kuze kube sekupheleni kukaMfumfu 2019.
Uma u-Eskom engahluleka ukukhokha imali ethile abolekwe yona lokho kungaholela ekutheni athathwe njengenkampani ehlulekile ukukhokhela zonke ezinye izikweletu zakhe futhi lokho kungaba nomthelela omkhulukazi emgodlagodleni wezimali zikahulumeni, kakade obhekene nesimo sokuntuleka nokushoda kwezimali.
Ngakho-ke, kumele sizame ukugwema le nkinga ngokuthi sethule ngokushesha uMthethosivivinywa Wesabelomali Esikhethekile ukuze sinike u-Eskom, eminyakeni yokuqala, ingxenye enkulu yalesi samba samabhiliyoni angama-230 amarandi oxhasomali azoludinga eminyakeni eyi-10 ezayo.
Lokhu sizokwenza ngoba phela u-Eskom ubaluleke kakhulu emnothweni wezwe, ukuthi singavele simyeke nje afadalale, ahluleke nokwenza umsebenzi wakhe. U-Eskom ungumthwalo wethu sonke njengesizwe futhi kumele siqinisekise ukuthi siyameseka.
Eminye imininingwane ephathelene nalokhu izohlinzekwa nguNgqongqoshe Wezezimali ngokuhamba kwesikhathi.
Khona maduze nje sizoqasha iSikhulu Esiyinhloko Yokuhlelwa Kabusha Kwenkampani, okulindeleke ukuthi siguqule futhi siphucule isimo sezimali sakwa-Eskom ngokuthi sicubungule ngokucophelela okukhulu uhlaka lwesimo sengeniso-mali, izikweletu kanye nezindleko zale nkampani.
Futhi u-Eskom usebenzisana nohulumeni kanye nabanye ababambiqhaza ukuze kubhekisiswe indlela eyakheke ngayo le nkampani, kanye nezikweletu zonke zenkampani kanjalo nemali ekweletwa ngomasipala kanye nabo bonke abanye abasebenzisi bakagesi kule nkampani.
Njengezwe, kumele siwugcizelele umgomo wokuthi labo abasebenzisa ugesi kumele bawukhokhele.
Ukungawukhokheli ugesi kubeka engcupheni uhlelo lonkana lokuphakelwa kukagesi, futhi kubeka engcupheni nomnotho wezwe, kuphazamise nemizamo yethu yokwakha amathuba omsebenzi.
Sezadlula izinsuku zokuduba kanye nokwenqaba ukukhokha. Manje sekuyisikhathi sokuthi sakhe, sekuyisikhathi sokuthi sonke sifake isandla.
Ukuze sikwazi ukuhlangabezana nemigomo yokukhulisa umnotho esizibekele yona, sizokwakha kabusha izisekelo zomnotho wethu ngokuvuselela nokwelula imikhakha yethu ekhiqizayo.
Lokhu kudinga ukuthi siqhamuke nendlela ehlukile yokwakha kabusha iqhingasu lethu lezimboni, sigqugquzele ngamandla utshalomali oluvela emkhakheni ozimele futhi sifake umdlandla embusweni ukuze sikhuthaze ukubandakanywa komuntu wonke emnothweni.
Lokhu kudinga futhi ukuthi uMbuso udlale indima yawo ngendlela efanele njengomvuli wamathuba nomphumelelisi wezinto ohlinzeka ngezidingongqangi kanye nengqalasizinda esemqoka, umlawuli oshaya imithetho eyakha futhi ivule amathuba ngokulinganayo kubo bonke ababambiqhaza, futhi njengomabi wezinto kabusha oqinisekisayo ukuthi bavikelekile futhi bayabhekelelwa labo ababuthakathaka futhi abasengcupheni ngoba bengakwazi ukuzinakekela kahle ngokwabo, abanikeze amathuba futhi abahlomise ukuze nabo bakwazi ukubonisa amakhono abo ngokuphelele futhi baphile impilo abayifunayo.
Sizogxila kakhudlwana futhi sibeke eqhulwini leyo mikhakha yomnotho ebonisa amathuba aphakeme okukhula.
Ngokusebenzisa izinhlelo zokuhlinzeka ngendawo yokuqhuba ibhizinisi, njengezizinda zomnotho ezikhethekile, ukuvuselelwa kwamapaki ezimboni endawo, izizinda zebhizinisi, izizinda zobuxhakaxhaka nobuchwepheshe besimanjemanje kanye namabhizinisi asemalokishini kanye nawasezindaweni ezisemakhaya, sizoletha intuthuko yezomnotho eduze kwezindawo okuhlala kuzona abantu. Sizogxila emabhizinisini asafufusa emadolobheni ethu, emalokishini kanye nasezindaweni ezisemakhaya futhi sakhe nezindawo zemakethe yokuhweba lapho osomabhizinisi bezothengisa khona imikhiqizo yabo.
Sizowukhulisa futhi siwunwebe kakhulu umkhakha wezolimo nokulungiswa kwemikhiqizo yezolimo ngokuthi sisekele uchungechunge lokukhiqizwa kanye nokulungiswa kwemikhiqizo yezolimo, sibheke amazwe nezindawo ezintsha esizothengisa kuzona imikhiqizo yethu futhi sinciphise ukuthembela kwethu emikhiqizweni yezolimo evela emazweni angaphandle.
Sizoyiqinisa futhi siyeseke imboni yezimayini ngokuthi sibheke amazwe nezindawo okuzothengiswa kuzona izimbiwa zaseNingizimu Afrika, ngokuthi silungise imikhiqizo yezimbiwa ethile, okuzokwenza ukuthi ikhuphuke ikhwalithi ngokunjalo nenanintengo laleyo mikhiqizo, sinciphise izindleko zokukhiqiza izimbiwa futhi sikhuphule nocwaningo kanye nokuthuthukiswa.
Ngokusebenzisa izinhlelo zokuhlinzeka ngendawo yokuqhuba ibhizinisi, njengezizinda zomnotho ezikhethekile, ukuvuselelwa kwamapaki ezimboni endawo, izizinda zebhizinisi, izizinda zobuxhakaxhaka nobuchwepheshe besimanjemanje kanye namabhizinisi asemalokishini kanye nawasezindaweni ezisemakhaya, sizoletha intuthuko yezomnotho eduze kwezindawo okuhlala kuzona abantu. Sizogxila emabhizinisini asafufusa emadolobheni ethu, emalokishini kanye nasezindaweni ezisemakhaya futhi sakhe nezindawo zemakethe yokuhweba lapho osomabhizinisi bezothengisa khona imikhiqizo yabo.
Sizoyifezekisa inhloso nesifiso sethu sokukhulisa ngokuphindwe kabili inani lezivakashi zakwamanye amazwe ezivakashela kuleli, liyifinyelele ezigidini ezingama-21 ngaphambi kowezi-2030.
Sizowukhulisa futhi siwunwebe kakhulu umkhakha wezolimo nokulungiswa kwemikhiqizo yezolimo ngokuthi sisekele uchungechunge lokukhiqizwa kanye nokulungiswa kwemikhiqizo yezolimo, sibheke amazwe nezindawo ezintsha esizothengisa kuzona imikhiqizo yethu futhi sinciphise ukuthembela kwethu emikhiqizweni yezolimo evela emazweni angaphandle.
Sizibophezele ekuqinisekiseni ukuthi izivakashi ezivakashela ezweni lethu ziphephile.
Sizoyikhulisa imboni yezobuchwepheshe nobuxhakaxhaka besimanjemanje ngokuthi siqinisekise ukuthi imithetho kanye nemithethonqubo elawulayo igqugquzela ukuqanjwa kwezinto ezintsha, sithuthukise amakhono abantu abasha kwezobuchwepheshe obusha, futhi sinciphise nezindleko ze-data. Nomaphi lapho besihamba khona, abantu abasha bebelokhu bekhalaza ngenkinga yezindleko ze-data eziphakeme kakhulu eNingizimu Afrika.
Ukuze sifake umfutho kule nqubo, kule nyanga ezayo, uNgqongqoshe Wezokuxhumana uzokhipha umyalelo oqondiswe oPhikweni Oluzimele Lwezokuxhumana LwaseNingizimu Afrika (i-Icasa) ukuthi luqalise inqubo yokuhlinzekwa kwamalayisensi omthamo wamagagasi okusakaza nokuthunyelwa kolwazi ngomoya.
Le nqubo izobandakanya izinyathelo zokukhuthaza ukuncintisana, uguquko, ukukhuliswa kwalo mkhakha ngendlela ebandakanya umuntu wonke kanye nokuqinisekisa ukufinyelela kwabantu bonke.
Lokhu kuyingxenye esemqoka ekwehliseni izindleko ze-data, okuyinto ebaluleke kakhulu ekuthuthukisweni komnotho kanjalo nasekuvulweni kwamathuba aqondiswe entsheni.
Siyayinxusa imboni yengqalasizinda yezokuxhumana ukuthi iphinde izehlise futhi izindleko ze-data ukuze inanintengo le-data lilingane nelamanye amazwe omhlaba.
Siyawuqinisa impela umkhankaso wethu wokuheha utshalomali.
Kutshalomali olungamabhiliyoni angama-300 amarandi olwamenyezelwa kwiNgqungquthela Yotshalomali yokuqala ngqa eyabanjwa ngonyaka odlule, kunemiklamo esiqalisiwe yenani elingaphezulu nje kancane kwamabhiliyoni angama-250 amarandi.
Siyaqhubeka nokwakha umgudu wotshalomali olungenayo kuleli, futhi lokhu kuzoboniswa kwiNgqungquthela yesibili Yotshalomali yaseNingizimu Afrika ezobanjwa kusukela mhla ziyisi-5 kuze kube ngumhla ziyisi-7 kuLwezi.
Esikhathini lapho sibhekene nongabazane, umsebenzi wamanxusa otshalomali sewuvule amaxhama okuxhumana nokusebenzisana asemqoka kakhulu phakathi kukahulumeni namabhizinisi.
Uma sibheka imbuyisambiko esiyithole kubona, kuyacaca ukuthi kusekuningi okusamele kwenziwe ngenhloso yokwenza ngcono isimo okusetshenzelwa ngaphansi kwaso esiphathelene nokutshalwa kwezimali.
Lokhu kubandakanya ukubuyekezwa kwendlela olawula ngayo umsebenzi wokuxazulula izinselelo abahlangabezana nazo abatshalizimali kanye nokuphucula nokuhlela kabusha inqubomgomo yokukhuthaza utshalomali kanye nohlaka lwesakhiwo sayo.
Mkhulu umsebenzi esesiwenzile ngaphansi koHlelo Lokukhulisa Umnotho Ngobambiswano phakathi Kukahulumeni Nomkhakha Ozimele oluholwa nguNgqongqoshe uNkosazana Dlamini-Zuma, uMnu Roelf Meyer kanye noDkt Johan van Zyl Slabbert.
Umkhakha ozimele usuthembise ukutshala imali engamabhiliyoni angama-840 amarandi emiklamweni engama-43 ngaphansi kwemikhakha eyi-19, futhi lokho kuzodala amathuba omsebenzi ayizi-155 000 kule minyaka emihlanu ezayo.
Ezingxoxweni ebezibanjwe nabamabhizinisi, uhulumeni usezwakalise ukuzibophezela ekususeni izithiyo nemigoqo ephathelene nezinqubomgomo nemithetho eyinkimbinkimbi futhi asheshise ukuqaliswa kwale miklamo.
Senza imizamo esheshayo yokuletha izinguquko ezisemqoka okuhloswe ngazo ukwenza kube lula ukwenza ibhizinisi kuleli, ngokuthi sihlanganise futhi sihlele kabusha imithethonqubo elawulayo, senze kube kula kakhulu ukuthola izimvume nokufaka izicelo ngobuchwepheshe besimanjemanje, futhi kuncishiswe nezindleko zokuthotshelwa kwenzinqubo ezibekiwe.
Ingqalasizinda ingumkhakha osemqoka kakhulu okumele kutshalwe kuwona izimali, osekela ukulethwa koguquko ezikhungweni, ukukhula komnotho kanye nokuvulwa kwamathuba omsebenzi.
Ingqalasiizinda ibaluleke kakhulu futhi ekuvuselelweni komnotho wezwe, kanye nokuletha nokuqalisa isikhathi esisha sokuvuselela nokuthuthukisa izwe lethu.
Indlela entsha esizoyilandela ekuthuthukisweni kwengqalasizinda isekelwe phezu kobambiswano oluqinile phakathi kukahulumeni nomkhakha ozimele, kanye nemiphakathi yendawo.
Lokhu kubandakanya inhlanganisela ekhethekile yezinyathelo eziphathelene nezimali kanye nalezo eziphathelene nokuphatha nokulawula okuhloswe ngazo ukukhuthaza umsebenzi wokwakha kanye nokubeka eqhulwini ukwakhiwa kwengqalasizinda yamanzi, imigwaqo kanye nezindlu zokuhlalisa abafundi, ngokuthi kusetshenziswe ngobunyoninco leyo mali eyabelwe le miklamo.
Njengoba kwamenyezelwa kwi-SoNa edlule, uhulumeni ubeke eceleni isamba esingamabhiliyoni ayi-100 amarandi ngenhloso yokuxhasa nokugqugquzela isiKhwama Sengqalasizinda.
Senza imizamo yokuthi lesi sikhwama sibe yisikhungo, esizolawulwa yiBhange Lentuthuko laseNingizimu Afrika (i-DBSA), futhi uMnyango Wezemisebenzi Yomphakathi kanye Nengqalasizinda ohlelwe kabusha yiwona ozoqapha umsebenzi owenziwa yilesi sikhungo.
Lokhu sikwenza ngokubonisana kanye nokubambisana nabatshalizimali abazimele, abafana nezikhungo ezilawula izikhwama zempesheni, ezingabatshalizimali abanentshisekelo ekubambeni iqhaza esiKhwameni Sengqalasizinda.
Lezi zinguquko zizoqinisekisa ukuhlelwa kangcono kwemiklamo yengqalasizinda, umsebenzi onohlonze wokuhlola ukuthi ingqalasizinda izokwenzeka ngempumelelo yini nokwenza amalungiselelo afanelekile, ukuphucula ukuphatha okukhethekile, ukuqaliswa ngobunyoninco kwemisebenzi yengqalasizinda kanye nokuphatha okuhle.
Lokhu kuhlinzekwa ngokwesekwa okudingeka kakhulu emkhakheni wezokwakha osekuphele isikhathi eside impela ufadalele.
Sizogqugquzela futhi sikhuthaze abantu ukuthi bathenge imikhiqizo nezimpahla ezikhiqizwe kuleli futhi sikhulise umkhakha wezokukhiqiza waseNingizimu Afrika ngokuthi siqinisekise ukuthi umkhankaso ‘Wokuthengwa Kwezimpahla Ezikhiqizwe Kuleli’ (i-‘Buy Local’) ungundabuzekwayo futhi ubonakala yonke indawo.
Siyabanxusa bonke abantu baseNingizimu Afrika ukuthi, ngenhloso futhi ngokuqhubekayo, bathenge izimpahla ezakhiwe kuleli.
Le sudu nehembe kanye nothayi engikugqokile namhlanje kwakhiwe ngabasebenzi bemboni yendwangu yaseNingizimu Afrika e-House of Monatic, khona lapha e-Salt River edolobheni laseKapa.
Sonke masithenge izimpahla ezakhiwe kuleli ukuze sikhulise isibalo sabantu abathenga impahla ekhiqizwe kuleli.
Kulo nyaka esiwuphethe, sifuna ukwenza izivumelwano nezitolo ezithengisa impahla ukuthi ziqinisekise ukuthi zithenga izimpahla ezikhiqizwe eNingizimu Afrika futhi ziyikhangise ngenkuthalo imikhiqizo emihle kakhulu eyakhiwe ngabasebenzi baseNingizimu Afrika.
Futhi kusenjalo sizokhangisa ngomdlandla omkhulu imikhiqizo yethu ezwekazini lase-Afrika kanye nasemhlabeni wonke jikelele.
Lezi zinyathelo zisekelwe phezu kwesibophezelo sethu esiqinile kwinqubomgomo yomnotho-jikelele kanye neyezezimali ezoqhubeka nokukhuthaza ukwethenjwa kwaleli lizwe futhi kukhuthaze nokutshalwa kwezimali.
Sizibophezele ekubolekeni izimali ngobuhlakani obukhulu ukuze singaboleki imali engaphezu kwamandla ethu okukhokha leyo mali esiyibolekile futhi sizibophezele ekusebenziseni imali ngokucophelela okukhulu ukuze siqinisekise uzinzo ezimalini zikahulumeni futhi sinciphise nesikweletu sezwe.
IBhange Lombuso laseNingizimu Afrika lisiyikhungo esisemqoka kakhulu ezweni lethu elibuswa ngentando yeningi labantu, esithenjwayo futhi esihlonishwa kakhulu kuleli nasemhlabeni wonke jikelele.
Uzinzo lwamananintengo luyadingeka impela, kepha-ke alwanele ekuqinisekiseni ukukhula komnotho.
Amananintengo ezimpahla nezinsizakalo adlondlobalayo anciphisa amandla okuthenga abo bonke abantu baseNingzimu Afrika, ikakhulukazi labo abadla imbuya ngothi.
Ukwehla kwamandla emali kunciphisa amandla okuncintisana ezimpahla zakuleli ezithunyelwa emazweni angaphandle kanye namafemu akuleli akhiqiza izimpahla ezincintisana nezimpahla ezingena kuleli ezakhiwe kwamanye amazwe, futhi lokhu kubeka engcupheni izimboni zakuleli kanye nemisebenzi.
Ngenxa yalesi sizathu-ke, uMthethosisekelo wethu ugunyaza iBhange Lombuso laseNingizimu Afrika ukuthi livikele isilinganisontengo semali yakuleli ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukukhula komnotho okulingene futhi okusimeme.
Namuhla, sithanda ukuligcizelela leli gunya elihlinzekwe ngokomthethosisekelo, okumele lifezekiswe yiBhange Lombuso ngokuzimela, ngaphandle kokuchema noma ukucwasa.
UMthethosisekelo wethu uyalela futhi ukuthi kube nokubonisana okuqhubekayo phakathi kwebhangengodla kanye noNgqongqoshe Wezezimali ukuze kugqugquzelwe ukusebenza ngendlela ehambelanayo emnothweni wezwe wonkana, ngenhloso yokuqinisekisa ukwakhiwa kwamathuba omsebenzi kanye nokukhulisa umnotho.
Uma sifuna ukuncintisana ngempumelelo namazwe omhlaba, futhi uma sifuna ukuheha utshalomali, kumele sithathe izinyathelo zokunciphisa izindleko eziphakeme kakhulu zokwenza ibhizinisi eNingizimu Afrika, futhi sixegise imithethonqubo nemidanti eyinkimbinkimbi futhi ewundendende okumele ilandelwe.
Kumele sifinyelele esigabeni lapho ingekho neyodwa inkampani okumele ilinde isikhathi esingaphezu kwezinyanga eziyisithupha ngaphambi kokuthi ithole imvume noma ilayisensi yokusebenza futhi kumele kube yinto elula nje ukubhalisa inkampani entsha ngosuku olulodwa nje vo.
Sizoqhubeka nokunciphisa izindleko zokwenza ibhizinisi ngokuthi sinciphise intela yezimpahla ezithunyelwa emazweni angaphandle, sizame ukuthola nokusebenzisa izindlela zokuphehla ugesi ezishimbile, futhi senze umkhakha wokuthutha impahla ngezitimela ube sesimweni sokuncintisana neminye imikhakha yokuthuthwa kwempahla futhi usebenze ngobunyoninco.
Ngokuholwa yi-NDP, kungumthwalo nomsebenzi wethu ukuqinisekisa intuthuko ebandakanya umuntu wonke futhi esimeme, ezokwazi ukumelana nokuguquguquka kwesimo sezulu.
Ngokubambisana nomkhakha ozimele, abasebenzi kanye namazwe omhlaba sizoqinisa futhi sikhuphule imizamo yethu yokumelana nokuguquguquka kwesimo sezulu futhi sinciphise nomthelela omubi walokhu.
Sinethuba lokuqinisekisa ukuthi sihamba phambili emizamweni yokukhulisa umnotho ngendlela ebhekelela futhi inakekele imvelo, sibe nezimboni ezisebenzisa izindlela-kusebenza ezikhiqiza ikhabhoni encane kakhulu futhi ezingawuncolisi umkhathi nemvelo, sihambe phambili ekusetshenzisweni kobuchwepheshe obusha futhi sithathe amagxathu amakhulukazi aphokophele emnothweni wangomuso.
Kumele siwukhulise umthamo wamandla kagesi ovuselelekayo futhi ongayingcolisi imvelo, kwizinhlobo zemithombo kagesi ehlukahlukene esetshenziswa kule lizwe, futhi sizame ukucubungula nokubhekisisa ukuthi ngeke yini kube wusizo ukuthi siguqukele emnothweni ogxile kakhulu ekusetshenzisweni kwegesi ihayidrojini.
Ukukhula komnotho okusheshayo kudinga futhi ukuthi kusheshiswe izinguquko kwezomhlaba ezindaweni ezisemakhaya kanye nezosemadolobheni futhi kube khona inqubo-kusebenza ecacile ephathelene nokuphathwa kwamalungelo omhlaba.
Sesiwutholile umbiko weThimba Elikhethekile Lokweluleka uMongameli mayelana Nezinguquko Kwezomhlaba Nezolimo, elabe liholwa yiPhini likaMongameli, manje osuzokwethulwa phambi kweKhabhinethi ukuze ucutshungulwe.
Izincomo zaleli thimba elikhethekile yizona ezizosetshenziswa ukuhlanganisa nokuphothula uhlelo lwezinguquko kwezomhlaba olubanzi futhi oluzoletha uguquko olunohlonze.
Kulesi sikhashana esifushane esizayo, uhulumeni uzosheshisa imizamo yokuhlonza kanye nokwaba umhlaba kahulumeni okulungele ukuhlaliswa kwabantu ezindaweni ezisemadolobheni, onazo izinsiza nezidingongqangi zesimanjemanje, futhi uhulumeni uzokwaba nomhlaba ozosetshenziselwa ukulima.
Kwiphakheji yokukhuthaza nokuvuselela umnotho eyamenyezelwa ngonyaka odlule, sathembisa ukuthi sizokubeka eqhulwini ukuxhaswa ngezimali kwabalimi abasafufusa.
Kulesi sikhathi sesabelo esimaphakathi, iBhange Lomhlaba labelwe imali engamabhiliyoni ama-3.9 amarandi ngenhloso yokweseka nokuxhasa abalimi abamnyama abahwebayo.
Ingxenye esemqoka kakhulu yeqhingasu lokukhulisa umnotho leNingizimu Afrika wukudidiyelwa komnotho wakuleli neminotho yamazwe angomakhelwane kanye neminotho yamazwe aleli zwekazi lonkana.
Isizinda Sokuhwebelana Mahhala Kwamazwe Ezwekazi lase-Afrika, (i-AfCFTA), sizothuthukisa futhi senze ngcono ukuhamba nokuthunyelwa kwezimpahla kanye nezinsizakalo, ingqala-bhizinisi kanye nezinsiza-kusebenza zokukhiqiza impahla kwizwekazi lonkana.
Iqhingasu leNingizimu Afrika elivuseleliwe futhi lafakwa nomfutho ligxile ekukhuliseni ubudlelwano bokuhwebelana nokutshalwa kwezimali phakathi kwelizwe lethu nesifunda sonkana samazwe aseNingizimu ye-Afrika kanye nezwekazi lonkana.
Ngaphakathi kweNhlangano Yokuthuthukiswa Kwamazwe aseNingizimu ye-Afrika (i-SADC), sizobeka eqhulwini uchungechunge lokulungiswa kwemikhiqizo kanye nokuthunyelwa nokuhanjiswa kwayo phakathi kwamazwe angaphansi kwale nhlangano, okuyimikhiqizo yemikhakha enjengowezamandla, owezimayini nokuthuthukiswa kwekhwalithi yemikhiqizo yezimbiwa, owezokukhiqizwa kwempahla, owezengqalasizinda kanye nowokulungiswa kwemikhiqizo yezolimo.
Ukukhula komnotho wezwe ngeke neze kuwenze umehluko ophawulekayo uma kungalekeleli ekwakhiweni kwamathuba omsebenzi amaningi.
Njengoba izinga lokuntuleka kwamathuba omsebenzi entsheni lingaphezu kwama-50% kusho ukuthi izwe libhekene nengwadla enkulukazi edinga ukuthi kutholakale izixazululo eziphuthumayo, ezihambisana nokusetshenziswa kwamaqhingasu amasha futhi ezihambelanayo, lapho wonke umuntu kumele akubone njengento edingekayo futhi esemqoka kakhulu ukuthi kusetshenzwe ngokubambisana.
Futhi njengoba abantu abasha bengena ngobuningi minyaka yonke esigabeni sabantu abathungatha amathuba omsebenzi, umnotho wezwe kumele wakhe amathuba omsebenzi aqondiswe entsheni angaphezulu kakhulu kwamathuba avulekayo njengamanje; ngenhloso nje yokuqinisekisa ukuthi alidlondlobali ngokweqile izinga lokuntuleka kwamathuba omsebenzi entsheni.
Iqiniso elimsulwa wukuthi mayelana nenkinga yokuntuleka kwamathuba omsebenzi entsheni, kumele senze imizamo enohlonze futhi ephuthumayo, ngenhloso nje yokunciphisa amanani aphakeme kakhulu esibhekene nawo njengamanje entsha ehleli emakhaya engasebenzi, singakayibali intsha esazophuma ezikhungweni zemfundo, nayo ifune umsebenzi.
Ngakho-ke kusemqoka kakhulu ukuthi siluqalise ngokushesha okukhulu uhlelo olubanzi – oluqhutshwa futhi lulawulwe yiHhovisi likaMongameli – ukuze kwakhiwe amathuba amasha omsebenzi aqondiswe entsheni, angekho ngaphansi kwezigidi ezimbili kule minyaka eyi-10 ezayo.
Lolu hlelo luzosebenza kuyo yonke iminyango kahulumeni futhi lusebenze kuzona zontathu izigaba zikahulumeni, ngokubambisana nabomkhakha ozimele.
Sesiqalile kakade ukusebenzisana nabomkhakha ozimele ekwakheni imigudu yokufaka abantu abasha emsebenzini ngokuthi sikhulise futhi sithuthukise izinhlelo ezikhona njengamanje zokuphathwa kwemigudu yokufakwa kwentsha emsebenzini.
Lezi yizinhlelo ezivumela labo bantu abasha ababhalise ngaphansi kwazo ukuthi babonakale kalula, bathole ukwesekwa kanye namathuba azokwenza ukuthi bavele obala ukuze babonakale kalula ukuthi badinga amathuba omsebenzi noma amathuba okusungula amabhizinisi.
Lezi zinhlelo ziyaqinisekisa ukuthi intsha evela emakhaya ahlwempu – futhi ikakhulukazi abesifazane abasebasha – iyahlonyiswa futhi icijwe ngendlela efanele ukuze ikwazi ukuwabamba ngazo zombili amathuba amasha avelayo.
Uhulumeni uzoqhubeka nokuhlinzeka amathuba omsebenzi ngaphansi koHlelo Olunwetshiwe Lwemisebenzi Yomphakathi (i-EPWP), ikakhulukazi emikhakheni edinga abasebenzi abaningi njengomkhakha wokulungiswa kwengqalasizinda, ukuhlakulwa kokhula nokususwa kwezihlahla nezitshalo ezingadingekile, ukuvalwa kwamapayipi amanzi avuzayo kanye nokwakhiwa kwemigwaqo.
Sizoqhubeka nokuthuthukisa izinhlelo zokuqinisekisa ukuthi abantu abasha abangasebenzi bakulungele ukusebenza futhi bayafakwa emsebenzini kuleyo mikhakha lapho kunamathuba omsebenzi akhulayo.
Le mikhakha ibandakanya imikhakha enjengowezinsizakalo zamazwe ngamazwe zokuhlinzeka usizo ngocingo, uchungechunge lomsebenzi wokulungiswa kwemikhiqizo yezolimo, ukuxhunywa kwemishini yezobuchwepheshe, ukulungiswa nokugcinwa kwemishini isesimweni sokusebenza esihle kanye namathuba amasha ahlinzekwa ngumnotho wezobuxhakaxhaka nobuchwepheshe besimanjemanje kanye noGuquko Lwezimboni Lwesine Olugxile Ekusetshenzisweni Kobuchwepheshe Besimanjemanje.
Uhulumeni uzoqhubeka futhi nokuqinisekisa ukuthi abantu abasha bayaqashwa ezinhlanganweni nasezikhungweni zomphakathi ezinjengezikhungo zokuthuthukiswa kwezingane zisencane kanye nezinhlangano ezihlinzeka ngosizo lwezempilo nokunakekelwa.
Sizolukhulisa uHlelo Lukazwelonke Lokuvulwa Kwemisebenzi Eqondiswe Entsheni ukuze luqashe abantu abasha abayizi-50 000 njalo ngonyaka.
Uhulumeni uzosekela futhi axhase izinhlelo-kusebenza zobuchwepheshe eziqondiswe kubantu abasha abangosomabhizinisi ezindaweni zasemakhaya kanye nasemalokishini.
Sizozikhulisa izinhlelo zethu ukuze silekelele abantu abasha bakwazi ukuthola ulwazi nesipiliyoni somsebenzi lapho bezokwenza umsebenzi abazowuholela, ngaphansi kwezinhlelo ezinjengohlelo loPhiko Lokuqashwa Kwentsha (i-YES), futhi silekelele intsha ekutholeni amathuba okuqeqeshelwa emsebenzini.
Sizohlinzeka ngezizinda zokulekelela nokuhlinzeka ngosizo emabhizinisini amancane ngenhloso yokunikeza abantu abasha izeluleko eziphathelene nezimali kanye nokuqhutshwa kwebhizinisi ngenkathi besungula amabhizinisi abo.
Izolo, kube yintokozo enkulu kimina ukuhlangana nokuxoxisana neqenjana labantu abasha baseNingizimu Afrika abenza umsebenzi omuhle kakhulu ekwakheni izwe lethu kanye nokuthuthukisa abantu bakithi.
Bangosomabhizinisi, abathuthukisi bomphakathi, izishoshovu kanye namaciko.
Enye yezinto ezisemqoka esizifundile kulezi zingxoxo ebesizibambe nentsha yaleli lizwe wukuthi akumele siqhamuke nezixazululo ezicatshangwa yithina bese sithi mabazisebenzise: konke esikwenzayo kumele kuholwe ngabantu abasha ngokwabo.
Basitshelile ukuthi yini abayifunayo, futhi yini abayidingayo.
Yebo, bayakufuna impela ukuqashwa, kepha-ke futhi bafuna nokuba ngabaqashi ngokwabo.
Baqhamuke nemiqondo-mbono eminingi futhi ehlukahlukene, bahamba phambili ekusetshenzisweni kwezindlela-kusebenza ezintsha, futhi bafuna ukuzenzela izinto ngokwabo.
Kumele siyeseke le ntshisekelo yentsha ekusunguleni amabhizinisi ngoba phela impumelelo yaleli lizwe incike emdlandleni wabantu abasha kanye nasethalenteni labo lokuqhamuka nemiqondo emisha kanye nezindlela-kusebenza ezintsha.
Ukuze sikwazi ukuqinisekisa ukuthi kule minyaka eyi-10 ezayo zonke izingane ezineminyaka eyi-10 ziyakwazi ukufunda futhi zikuqonda kahle lokho ezikufundayo, kumele sigqugquzele isizwe sonke ukuthi siweseke umkhankaso omkhulukazi wokufunda.
Ukufunda kwengane isencane kuyinto eyisisekelo, futhi ukuphumelela nokuqhubekela phambili kwengane emfundweni yayo kuncike kulokhu; kusukela esikoleni kuqhubeke njalo kuyongena emfundweni ephakeme kuze kuyofinyelela nasemsebenzini imbala.
Zonke ezinye izinhlelo zethu – kusukela emsebenzini owenziwayo ukwenza ngcono izinga lemfundo eyisisekelo kuyofinyelela ekuhlinzekweni kwemfundo ephakeme yamahhala kubantu abahlwempu, kusukela kutshalomali nokwesekwa esikunikeza amakolishi ezoBuchwepheshe Nemisebenzi Yobungoti Bezandla kuyofinyelela ekukhulisweni kwezinhlelo zokuqeqeshelwa emsebenzini – ngeke neze zikhiqize imiphumela emihle uma singaqali ngokuqinisekisa ukuthi izingane ziyakwazi ukufunda.
Yizinhlelo ezinjengoMkhankaso Wokufunda Kazwelonke ezizokwenza sikwazi ukuqhuba ngempumelelo lo mzamo owenziwa ezweni lonkana.
Bonke othisha bezinga eliyisisekelo kanye nelimaphakathi bazoqeqeshelwa ukufundisa isiNgisi kanye nezilimi zaBomdabu, futhi njengamanje siqeqesha amaqembu abaqeqeshi esizobathumela ezikoleni ukuthi bayohlinzeka ngosizo olusezingeni eliphezulu kothisha ngaphakathi esikoleni.
Siqalisa uHlelo Lokufunda Emabangeni Aphansi, olubandakanya izinhlelo zesifundo ezinako konke, izincwadi zokufunda ezengeziwe kanye nosizo longoti kothisha beZinga Eliyisisekelo.
Lokhu kuyingxenye yemizamo ebanzi yokuqinisa uhlelo lwemfundo eyisisekelo ngokucija nokuhlomisa amathimba abaphathi bezikole, siphucule amakhono othisha futhi siqinisekise ukusetshenziswa kwendlela ethembakele yokukala inqubekelaphambili yabafundi ebangeni lesithathu, elesithupha kanye nelesishiyagalolunye.
Kumele futhi abantu abasha sibacijele imisebenzi yangomuso.
Yingakho, ezikoleni zamabanga aphansi, sethula izifundo enjengomsebenzi wokwakhiwa kwamakhodi ezinhlelo-kusebenza zamakhompyutha (izifundo ze-coding) kanye nomsebenzi wokuhlola nokuhlaziya i-data (i-data analytics).
