Ukufezekiswa kwazo zonke lezi zinjongo kudinga uMbuso onamandla nekhono lokusebenza kanye nezinsiza-kusebenza ezidingekayo, futhi othuthukisayo.
Lowo akuwona nje uMbuso ohlinzeka kuphela ngezikhungo kanye nengqalasizinda ezokwenza ukuthi umnotho wezwe kanye nomphakathi usebenze, kodwa nguMbuso onezindlela-kusebenza zokuletha uguquko.
Ngasekuqaleni kwale nyanga, samemezela ukuhlelwa kabusha kweminyango kahulumeni eminingana ukuze ikwazi ukwenza kahle imisebenzi ethweswe yona.
Isinqumo sethu besisekelwe phezu komzamo wokuqiniseksa ukusebenza ngobunyoninco, ukunciphisa izindleko, ukuphatha ngokubambisana kanye nokuhambelanisa imisebenzi eyenziwa yiminyango kahulumeni ehlukahlukene.
Lokhu kuyisiqalo senqubo ebanzi yokunqanda ukufadalala kwamandla okusebenza oMbuso kanye nokuhlela kabusha uhlelo-kusebenza lwethu lokuhlinzeka ngezidingo-ngqangi ukuze lukwazi ukuzisebenzela kahle kakhulu izakhamuzi zezwe lethu.
Sizosebenzisa inqubo-kusebenza ezogxila ezifundeni ezingama-44 nemikhandlu-dolobha eyisishiyagalombili ngenhloso yokusheshisa ukuhlinzekwa kwezidingo-ngqangi, futhi kuqinisekiswe ukuthi omasipala bahlinzekwa ngokwesekwa okufanelekile futhi banikezwe nezinsiza-kusebenza ezanele.
Ngenhloso yokuqinisekisa ukuthi uMbuso uyakwazi ukuletha kahle intuthuko kwezomnotho kanye nakwezenhlalo yomphakathi, kusemqoka kakhulu ukuthi siqinise amaBhizinisi Ombuso (ama-SOE).
Ngokusebenzisa uMkhandlu KaMongameli wama-SOE, uhulumeni uhlose ukuqinisekisa ukusebenza ngendlela ehambelanayo phakathi kwazo zonke izinkampani zombuso futhi kucaciswe kahle namagunya nemisebenzi ezethweswe yona ngokuhlukahlukana kwazo.
Sizokwakhela phezu komsebenzi osuqalisiwe kakade okuhloswe ngawo ukuxazulula izinkinga zokungaphathi ngendlela efanele, nokuhluleka ukusebenza ngobunyoninco kanye nezinkinga eziphathelene nokusimama ngakwezezimali.
Sizibophezele ekwakheni uMbuso olandela izinkambiso zokusebenza ngobuqotho lapho ingekho nakancane inkohlakalo, ukwenzelela, ukuzicebisa ngokungemthetho, kanye nokweba imali kahulumeni.
Sifuna ukuba neqembu labasebenzi bakahulumeni abanekhono, abasebenza ngobungoti futhi abenza umsebenzi wabo ngobuqotho obukhulu futhi abazinikele emsebenzini wabo wokusebenzela umphakathi.
Seziqalile ukukhiqiza imiphumela emihle futhi esemqoka izinyathelo esizithathile zokuqeda ukubanjwa ngobhongwane kombuso kanye nokulwisana nenkohlakalo, kubandakanya nezinyathelo zokuqinisa uPhiko Lukazwelonke Lwezokushushisa (i-NPA), uPhiko Lokuphenywa Kwamacala Akhethekile (i-SIU), uPhiko Lokuqoqwa Kwentela lwaseNingizimu Afrika (i-SARS) kanye neNhlangano Kahulumeni Yezokuvikela.
Kepha-ke usemningi impela umsebenzi okumele wenziwe.
Sesinxuse uMqondisi Kazwelonke Wezokushushiswa Komphakathi (i-NDPP) ukuthi athuthukise uhlelo oluzophucula futhi luthuthukise kakhudlwana amandla okusebenza kanye nobunyoninco be-NPA, kubandakanya nokuqinisekisa ukuthi uqhutshwa kahle futhi ngobunono umsebenzi wokudliwa kwempahla etholakale ezenzweni zobugebengu nenkohlakalo.
Kumele siqinisekise ukuthi iyabuyiswa imali kahulumeni entshontshiwe ukuze isetshenziselwe ukuhlinzeka izidingo-ngqangi kanye nengqalasizinda eyisisekelo edingeka kakhulu emiphakathini edla imbuya ngothi.
Sibheke ukuthi iNkantolo entsha Ekhethekile ye-SIU iqale umsebenzi wayo kulezi zinyanga ezimbalwa ezizayo ngenhloso yokusheshisa amacala okudliwa kwempahla ahlobene nophenyo lwe-SIU, njengamanje alinganiselwa kwinani-bungako elingamabhiliyoni ayi-14.7 amarandi.
INingizimu Afrika izoqhubeka nokudlala indima esemqoka kwezobudlelwane bamazwe omhlaba emizamweni yokuqinisekisa ukuthula nokuvikeleka emhlabeni, intuthuko egxile kubantu kanye nokuchuma nokuphumelela kwabantu bonke.
Siyakuvuselela ukuzibophezela kwethu ekusebenzisaneni okuhle namazwe omhlaba ngenhloso yokugcina nokuvikela uhlelo lokubambisana nokusebenzisana kwamazwe ngamazwe olusekelwe phezu kwemithetho ebekiwe, oluholwa yiNhlangano Yezizwe (i-UN).
Sizosebenzisa isikhundla sethu njengelungu loMkhandlu Wezokuvikela we-UN, (i-UNSC), ukugqugquzela imizamo yokuxazulula izingxabano ngokuthula, ikakhulukazi kwizwekazi lase-Afrika
Ukuze sikwazi ukufinyelela kuhlobo lweNingizimu Afrika esiyifisayo, sidinga isivumelwano sokusebenzisana nokubambisana esisha.
Kudingeka ukuthi sakhe ubambiswano oluqinile phakathi kukahulumeni, abasebenzi, imiphakathi kanye nezinhlangano zomphakathi.
Lokhu kubeka umthwalo emahlombe ethu sonke.
Uhulumeni kumele akhe isimo esifanelekile, azisebenzise ngobuhlakani izinsiza nezimali zakhe futhi atshale izimali ekuthuthukiseni abasebenzi baleli lizwe.
Kungaba yinto enhle impela uma abamabhizinisi bengazibhekelela izinjongo zezwe ezisemqoka kanye nezidingo zomphakathi ngenkathi bethatha izinqumo kanye nezinyathelo zabo.
Siyavuma ukuthi izinyunyana zabasebenzi kumele zilwele amalungelo abasebenzi, futhi kusenjalo, zigqugquzele ukusimama kwamabhizinisi nokwakhiwa kwamathuba omsebenzi.
Izinhlangano zomphakathi wonkana kumele ziqhubeke nokudlala indima yazo yokuqinisekisa ukuthi uhulumeni uyaphendula ngemisebenzi yakhe, kodwa futhi kumele zihlanganyele nathi ekuthatheni izinyathelo eziphathekayo okuhloswe ngazo ukufezekisa izinjongo zethu sonke.
Sinethemba lokuthi amaqembu amelwe kuleli Phalamende azoba yingxenye esemqoka kulolu bambiswano, futhi alekelele, ahlinzeke ngemibono enohlonze nemiqondo ebonisa ubuhlakani obukhulu futhi aqhamuke nezixazululo kanye nemizamo ephathekayo ngenhloso yokuhlomulisa izwe lonkana.
Lesi sivumelwano sokubambisana komphakathi wonkana sidinga ukuthi wonke umuntu afake isandla.
Futhi sidinga ukuzidela kanye nokuhlangabezana phakathi, ukuze kube khona ukuvumelana nokusebenzisana okuhle.
Impumelelo yomuntu wonke incike kwindlela aziphatha ngayo omunye nomunye wethu.
Ukuze sikwazi ukuvuselela nokufaka ugqozi nofuqufuqu ekuqalisweni kwe-NDP, kumele siqinisekise ukuthi amehlo ethu ahlala ethe njo phambili lapho siphokophele khona.
Sifuna iNingizimu Afrika lapho wonke muntu ezophila kamnandi futhi ahlale ngokunethezeka, akhombe ngophakathi.
Kodwa-ke futhi sifuna iNingizimu Afrika lapho sizokwazi ukusebenzisa ngokuphelele amandla namakhono ethu ngenkathi siqhubeka endleleni ephokophele phambili.
Sifuna iNingizimu Afrika ebeke eqhulwini izinhlelo zayo zokuthutha ngesitimela futhi okuyizinhlelo ezikhiziqa izitimela ezihamba ngesivinini esikhulu ezizoxhumanisa amadolobhakazi ethu nezindawo zasemakhaya ezisemajukujukwini ezwe lethu.
Kumele sizibone ngamehlo engqondo sesiphila ezweni lapho izitimela ezihamba ngesivinini esikhulu zidlula eGoli ziphokophele e-Musina, futhi lapho zifika e-Buffalo City zithi ukuma kancane, zivela eThekwini, sezibuyela emuva lapha edolobheni laseKapa.
Sifuna iNingizimu Afrika enomnotho ogxile kubuchwepheshe besimanjemanje lapho sisebenzisa khona izindlela-kusebenza zezempilo ezihlinzekwa ngohlelo-kusebenza lwe-inthanethi, nama-robotics kanye nokwelashwa okuhlinzekwa ezigulini ezikude kwezindawo zokwelapha, ngenkathi siqalisa ukusebenza kwe-NHI.
Sifuna iNingizimu Afrika engagcini nje kuphela ngokuthumela kwamanye amazwe imikhiqizo engakalungiswa, kepha eyisizinda esisezingeni lomhlaba sokukhiqizwa kwezingxenye ezisemqoka ezisetshenziswa kuma-elekthronikhi, ezimotweni kanye nakumakhompyutha.
Kumele sibe yizwe elikwaziyo ukuzondla futhi lokhu sikwenze ngokusebenzisa ubuchwepheshe besimanjemanje kwezolimo.
Kuyiphupho lami ukubona iNingizimu Afrika lapho kwakhiwa idolobha elisha sha esikhathini sombuso wentando yeningi labantu, elinamabhilidi amade, izikole, amanyuvesi, izibhedlela kanye namafemu.
Leli phupho lami ligqugquzelwe yingxoxo engibe nayo nabantu abanohlonze abanjengoDkt Nkosazana Dlamini-Zuma, Dkt Naledi Pandor, Nkz Jessie Duarte kanye noMongameli wase-China u-Xi Jinping, owathi uma engixoxela ngokuthi i-China imatasa yakha idolobha elisha ebangeni elingamakhilomitha ayi-100 kusuka edolobheni lase-Beijing, wangenza ngibone ukuthi ngempela lingafezekiseka leli phupho lami.
Leli yiphupho okungaba ngelethu sonke futhi silifezekise ngempela.
Eminyakeni eyi-25 leli lizwe libuswa ngentando yeningi labantu, asikaze sakhe idolobha elisha.
Bangama-75% abantu baseNingizimu Afrika abazobe sebehlala ezindaweni ezisemadolobheni ngowezi-2030.
Amadolobha anjengeGoli, i-Tshwane, iKapa kanye neTheku aseqala ukuphelelwa yindawo yokuhlalisa bonke abantu abafudukela ngobuningi emadolobheni.
Ingabe asikafiki yini isikhathi sokuthi sibonise isibindi futhi senze lokho ebesingacabangi neze ukuthi singaba namandla okukwenza?
Ngithanda ukumema abantu baseNingizimu Afrika ukuthi baqale ukubona ngamehlo ukwakhiwa kwedolobha elinjengaleli.
Thina siyisizwe saseNingizimu Afrika, esikwaziyo ukuthi ngoMthethosisekelo waso, sibuyise ithemba esimweni lapho belingasekho nelincane ithemba, esikwaziyo ukuhlinzeka ngamalungelo kubantu ababephucwe konke okungokwabo basala bengondinga sithebeni, futhi siyisizwe elikwaziyo ukuhlinzeka ngokunethezeka nokuvikeleka kubo bonke abantu balo, amadoda, abesifazane kanye nezingane.
Nakuba kukhona lapho sihlulekile ukwenza izinto ngendlela efanele kanye nalapho siphelelwe khona wugqozi nofuqufuqu, asikazikhohlwa ukuthi singobani futhi asikakhohlwa ukuthi simeleni.
Siseyisona leso sizwe esishiwo ngenhla.
Ungazibuza ukuthi ngingaba kanjani nethemba ezikhathini ezinzima njengalezi.
Nginethemba ngoba sengihambe ibanga elide nabantu baleli lizwe – abahlengikazi kanye nabasebenzi bezempilo, amaphoyisa namasosha, othisha ezikoleni zethu abafundi abazimisele ukuphumelela nakuba bebhekene nobunzima nenhlupheko emakhaya, kanye nentsha ezama ukuzisungulela amabhizinisi, ezama ukuqamba nokwakha izinto ezitsha, futhi eyenza konke okusemandleni ayo ukuphumelela ngaphansi kwezimo ezinzima ehlangabezana nazo.
Yinina-ke eninginikeza isibindi, futhi nami ngokunjalo ngininikeza isibindi.
Uma sisebenza ngokubambisana akukho okungasehlula, futhi akukho esingeke siphumelele kukona.
Njengoba singena esikhathini esisha, masithole ugqozi nesibindi emazwini ka-Ben Okri, uma ethi:
Will you be at the harvest,
Among the gatherers of new fruits?
Then you must begin today to remake
Your mental and spiritual world,
And join the warriors and celebrants
Of freedom, realizers of great dreams.
You can’t remake the world
Without remaking yourself.
Each new era begins within.
It is an inward event,
With unsuspected possibilities
For inner liberation.
We could use it to turn on
Our inward lights.
We could use it to use even the dark
And negative things positively.
We could use the new era
To clean our eyes,
To see the world differently,
To see ourselves more clearly.
Only free people can make a free world.
Infect the world with your light.
Help fulfil the golden prophecies.
Press forward the human genius.
Our future is greater than our past.
Without remaking yourself.
